I personally am viewing EQ as a training experience (though I happen to enjoy it, the advantages outweigh the disadvantages so far) while I collect notes on my ideal MMORPG.  I may never see everything I want, but at least now I have a list of what I want so I can keep my eyes open for it.<P>I'm sure as time passes and the genre matures there will be many more (and better) options.  Mistakes made in the code that are nearly impossible to fix in this game will be avoided in the next generation.  I'm looking forward to seeing that.   <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>Evenstar
